      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Mengakibatkan 2 poin </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_8727735731577178883.png",
                "id": "talent88704",
                "key": "Origin",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Origin"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Memanggil <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Eye of Stormy Judgment</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/c29fd0841f95e044bae32d03dc31765a_6424556467278208240.png",
                "id": "talent71902",
                "key": "Transcendence: Baleful Omen",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Transcendence: Baleful Omen"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>. Semua Karakter lain milikmu memperoleh 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Energy</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/8d02cb476ba0314a99ce5e7ecc3b4904_1614887162552319155.png",
                "id": "talent79092",
                "key": "Secret Art: Musou Shinsetsu",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Secret Art: Musou Shinsetsu"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>[Pasif] Saat pertandingan dimulai, Karakter ini memperoleh status <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Chakra Desiderata</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Chakra Desiderata</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Setelah Karakter lain milikmu menggunakan Elemental Burst:</span> Mendapatkan 1 poin \"Resolve\". (Maksimum dikumpulkan hingga 3 poin)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Karakter yang terpengaruh menggunakan Secret Art: Musou Shinsetsu:</span> Mengonsumsi semua poin \"Resolve\", setiap poin \"Resolve\" meningkatkan</p><p>DMG +1.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/f18816cd4d10b81b8610917baa51d71a_5458818368937281572.png",
                "id": "talent41176",
                "key": "Chakra Desiderata",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Chakra Desiderata"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai:</span> Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 3</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat berada dalam arena:</span> Elemental Burst Karakter milikmu mengakibatkan DMG +1.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7954280042448700996.png",
                "id": "talent81793",
                "key": "Eye of Stormy Judgment",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/75f1d2ef52221da67ee1c52ce97af966_8790657825139847899.png",
                "title": "Eye of Stormy Judgment"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Electro dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini, target berganti ke Karakter selanjutnya secara paksa</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] yang memberikan +1 poin DMG ke 2 kasus Dendro DMG atau Electro DMG berikutnya</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_8188250431188699224.png",
                "id": "talent3009",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Energy</span></strong></p><p>Karakter harus mengonsumsi Energy untuk menggunakan Elemental Burst-nya.</p><p>Saat Karakter menggunakan Elemental Skill atau Normal Attack, mereka akan memperoleh 1 poin Energy.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_8739942124620023982.png",
                "id": "talent91877",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detail Peraturan"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
